  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Project for Support of Kawar Economic Development</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective of this project is to contribute to the stability and peace of the Bilma (Kawar) region In Niger by providing positive prospects for youth. The two specific objectives are to promote social cohesion in the area of intervention, notably through the development of social dialogue and civic engagement of youth, and improve the economic opportunities and prospects for youth in the region. The project finances activities that build public confidence in the mechanisms of democratic participation and the capacities of youth to become actors of social cohesion and drivers of development. As such, the project focuses on the development of sport and culture through the funding of infrastructure and the organization of cultural and sporting events.</narrative>
  </description>
